(47, '<p>In information technology, networking is the construction, design, and use of a <a href="http://searchnetworking.techtarget.com/definition/network">network</a>, including the physical (cabling, <a href="http://searchnetworking.techtarget.com/definition/hub">hub</a>, <a href="http://searchsecurity.techtarget.com/definition/bridge">bridge</a>, <a href="http://searchtelecom.techtarget.com/definition/switch">switch</a>, <a href="http://searchnetworking.techtarget.com/definition/router">router</a>, and so forth), the selection and use of telecommunication <a href="http://searchnetworking.techtarget.com/definition/protocol">protocol</a> and computer software for using and managing the network, and the establishment of operation policies and procedures related to the network.</p>', '2016-01-28 12:54:16', 45, 6),
